    <item>
      <title>大众汽车表示，巴西可持续发展规则不应让汽车变得更加昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-sustainability-rules-should-not-make-cars-more-expensive-volkswagen-says-2024-02-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车巴西业务负责人西罗·波索博姆 (Ciro Possobom) 表示，巴西旨在促进该国汽车行业可持续发展投资的新激励计划需要避免使车辆变得更加昂贵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brazil-sustainability-rules-should-not-make-cars-more-expensive-volkswagen-says-2024-02-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 18:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国竞争的加剧，欧洲和美国汽车制造商竞相降低电动汽车成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-renault-race-cut-costs-make-evs-more-affordable-2024-02-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业高管周四表示，在中国竞争对手的压力下，美国和欧洲主要汽车制造商正在大力削减电动汽车成本，以便获得与化石燃料车型相似的价格标签和利润率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-renault-race-cut-costs-make-evs-more-affordable-2024-02-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 13:03:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
